### Step 10 — Board Policy (`src/policy.ts`)

```typescript
export function resolvePulseBoardGroupMatch(params: {
  groups?: Record<string, PulseBoardBoardConfig>;
  target: string;
}): { groupConfig?: PulseBoardBoardConfig; wildcardConfig?: PulseBoardBoardConfig }

export function resolvePulseBoardRequireMention(params: {
  groupConfig?: PulseBoardBoardConfig;
  wildcardConfig?: PulseBoardBoardConfig;
}): boolean
```

Mirror IRC's `policy.ts` pattern. Default `requireMention = false` for boards
(bulletin boards expect direct posts, unlike IRC where @ is needed).

